s of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/88652/', '', 'Quinidine, Amiodarone, Dronedarone, Lidocaine, Propafenone, Procainamide, Tocainide, Flecainide, Mexiletine, Dofetilide, Bretylium, More', 'Ketotifen, Levocetirizine, Cetirizine, Fexofenadine, Loratadine, Trimethobenzamide, Desloratadine, Azelastine', 1767369485);
